Located in the serene and upscale, Osborne Foreshore Estate, a highbrow gated community located along Osborne Road, Kara Residence is a luxury residential development that offers a collection of stunning 3-bedroom en-suite apartments and extensive leisure facilities including, a gymnasium, swimming pool, and a private courtyard. The project began in March 2020 following a groundbreaking ceremony steered by Moyo Ogunseinde, the Executive Director of the Kara Residence project developer, Uraga Real Estate Limited.  Speaking at the groundbreaking ceremony, Mr. Ogunseinde, said that one of the major ideas that triggered the development of the Kara Residence was the urge to create a serene space that would capture the essence and spirit of family living with timeless design. Also Read: Alexander Court Development in Ikoyi, Lagos, Nigeria In addition, he said the company’s expertise in design, planning, and execution had been fully utilized to deliver unique lifestyle products to its clients across the major real estate sector in Nigeria, ranging from hospitality to residential, and Kara Residence won’t be exceptional.  As a subsidiary of Honeywell Group, Uraga Real Estate Limited is a real estate company committed to creating long-lasting communities by providing creative and sustainable solutions.